{{Image}}
'''Infiltrator gloves''' were gloves equipped with an advanced [[Artificial intelligence/Legends|A.I.]] unit that the wearer could use to tap into nearby security or computer systems through cables or wireless transmission. The system also stabilized the wearer's hands for detail work, increasing their dexterity.

